text: Kylemore railway station is a proposed railway station to be built in the Ballyfermot area of Dublin, Ireland as part of the electrification of the South Western Commuter service from Dublin Heuston to Hazelhatch & Celbridge A tender was issued in June 2019 for the design of the electrification works, including those for the station. ==References== Category:Proposed railway stations in the Republic of Ireland
title: Kylemore railway station
